{"tid":940402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好心港女借出50蚊 無恥中國女唔還兼搶人手機","createTime":"2018-12-14T02:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T05:18:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8cf1abbba7f6b02b7dfdb23284aeea015b341a","tid":940402,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"大陸借錢黨愈趨猖獗，她們借不到錢更可能會搶&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有網民早前上載一段短片，指一名短髮、衣著光鮮的內地女聯同女同黨，在銅鑼灣如心酒店對出不斷向途人「借錢」。網民途經酒店，內地女隨即再向她「借錢」，網民拒絶並拿起電話，豈料內地女發惡欲搶去他的電話。<br />\n<br />\n片中兩名無恥內地女，原來早有前科，較早已向一名港女出手，聲稱要借50元吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n徐小姐向本刊透露，本月5日晚上11時許，她下班後往旺角新填地街乘車回家，其間遇見片中兩名說普通話的內地女人。徐小姐指二人起初問她附近有沒有食肆，又突然問她借錢，指她們的錢包遺漏在的士，想借50元應急。<br />\n<br />\n徐小姐起初不願借錢，但二人捉住她不放，才勉為其難借出50元。事後其中一個內地女人更問徐小姐聯絡電話，聲稱會還款，又互加微訊好友，指可以微訊支付還款。「她本身一開始說話好好聲氣，但後來便不理我了，我打電話給她亦不理我。」徐小姐這時方知被騙。<br />\n<br />\n徐小姐本身以為自己倒霉，豈料在網上又見到二人行騙，覺得十分生氣，「很令人討厭，你穿得一身光鮮還要伸大手掌向人討錢，騙取別人同情心！」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：亦安、艾馬<br />\n<br />\n攝影：田俊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20181213/large/1544689523_93d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544689523_93d6.jpg&h=01b1d73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名內地女人懷疑行騙不遂，欲搶去別人電話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20181213/large/1544692578_f2d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544692578_f2d2.jpg&h=3f68aa2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n騙徒聲稱會還款，會一直未有兌現承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/realtime/article/20181214/2_643299_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F2_643299_0&d=1zEXC4gEBXXb6dtK4q2adUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5d71b829\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F2_643299_0&h=8bccf002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/realtime/article/20181214/2_643299_0</a>"},{"pid":"67978b2e21da94c95e320c6ed506c25cc5774115","tid":940402,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"唔借就搶人手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好猖狂"},{"pid":"b966bae1439c7a39355cb70b88698c39c24d0fda","tid":940402,"uid":172507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係賤種打靶人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a4e10484d66104d5fe48f3e6131d828e06ef5a","tid":940402,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<br />\n<br />\n就算見到支那人行行下心臟病都咪撚幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76d65dcfb0d9c1257943aa0f14e5839ad2d7412","tid":940402,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"之後還喎，咁都信，仲要支那人"},{"pid":"69fa076888e338d4ce7b82647448cb5007e07bf2","tid":940402,"uid":187076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ksAo8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ksAo8u.jpg&h=9ffa430f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87831674069c376c68107533f9e023d7076bb61f","tid":940402,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58a4e10484d66104d5fe48f3e6131d828e06ef5a","tid":940402,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<br />\n<br />\n就算見到支那人行行下心臟病都咪撚幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"幫得就幫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji